<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Personally, I think these are pretty spiffy gloves.  I love these on my Rogue.  Sure, there might be better gloves out there...  But I always get asked about these when I get inspected.  (Also, a side note, in a old Multiplayer RPG/adventure I used to play online, Legends of Kesmai, there was a quest that was the pinnacle Monk-hood that was for Crystalline Gauntlets, whose icon was identical for the one on these. LoK was shutdown on May 29th, 2000, after it was bought by Electronic Arts, the Insert negative name here who run Ultima Online. *Moment of Silence for LoK*) <BR>
    Also, Tynen, Druzzil Ro's economy has alot of problems. Rare Items have trouble selling because few people know what they are.  There are alot less High levels on that server, and a great deal of them are from Fennin Ro.  <BR>
<BR>
I think most of that comes from being a young server, maybe hold onto the gauntlets for awhile...<BR>
